Coding of Speech at 8 kbit/s using Conjugate-Structure
Algebraic-Code-Excited Linear-Prediction (CS-ACELP) with
Voice Activity Decision(VAD), Discontinuous Transmission(DTX), 
and Comfort Noise Generation(CNG).


